Jane Connell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jane_Connell 0 Jane Sperry Connell (pronounced con-NELL, née Bennett; October 27, 1925 - September 22, 2013) was an American actress and singer. She was born in Berkeley, California, to Louis Wesley and Mary (née Sperry) Bennett.
